text: Þis synd þa land gemæra into dittune.
Of cranmeresþorne to blacan græfan, of þere blacan græfan on þa seofan æceras eastewearde.
Of þam seofan æceran on emenan, andlang emenan be healfan streame innan cytanforð.
Of cytanforða to tatan broke, of tatan broke on cwicelmeswyrþe eastewerde.
Þis is se wude on þes agan ende to byrlegate.
Fram wiðangate to cnuceshirste and to egænlea, fram ecganlæa to þam haran wyðie.
